results.locality: Long Reef Aquatic Reserve, Long Reef Aquatic Reserve has a wide variety of habitats, including sheltered boulder fields and surf-exposed ledges. If travelling by vehicle you can reach the Aquatic Reserve by driving along Anzac Avenue, Collaroy, to its eastern end at Long Reef Golf Course. You can also walk to the Aquatic Reserve by travelling north along the beach from Long Reef Surf Club or south along Collaroy Beach and around the rock baths.
